the inscertified courses currently available to more than 
250000 people a year who seek to become naturalized citizens are 
given through local school districts and nonprofit organizations 
the test itself is an oral exam not a written one and we 
only ask each applicant half a dozen to a dozen questions out of 
a list of 15 or 20 enough to satisfy the examiner that you know 
