toy that had many small parts a toy that gets packed away when 
the children are together 
when i have just one home like this they talk nonstop 
mrs joyce said that oneonone is important 
despite the push for individuality mrs joyce does dress the 
quintuplets alike sometimes if only for safety reasons if its 
a crowded place you can spot them in a minute and they can spot 
each other 
mothers day will be like any other day she said tending to 
the needs of the quintuplets 
the quints do draw attention mrs joyce said but thats not 
a problem most people love children and its usually a very 
amiable response 
i dont mind sharing the joy we were blessed and the 
children are healthy and happy 
