i have young kids myself its a good way of communicating 
mark niederkorn manager of kennedys market in decatur said 
saturday 
turnock said infant mortality is one of the major problems 
facing the state particularly in central and southern illinois 
illinois ranks among the top 10 states in infant death rates and 
is the worst among northern industrial states 
last year more than 2000 illinois babies died before reaching 
their first birthday the infant mortality rate equalled 115 
deaths per 1000 live births 
