april 29 after the label mixup was discovered however since 
then it has learned that thousands of bottles of the product have 
been distributed to consumers across the country as part of poison 
prevention week activities 
finding and returning those bottles is vital the fda says so 
that parents will not forget and accidentally give some of the 
eucalyptus oil to a child 
